&GLOBAL
  PROJECT P
  PROGRAM_NAME ATOM
&END GLOBAL
&ATOM
  ELEMENT P
  ELECTRON_CONFIGURATION [Ne] 3s2 3p3
  &METHOD
     METHOD_TYPE  KOHN-SHAM
     &XC
       &XC_FUNCTIONAL B3LYP
       &END XC_FUNCTIONAL
     &END XC
  &END METHOD
  &POTENTIAL
     CONFINEMENT_TYPE POLYNOM
     CONFINEMENT   0.2  8.0  2.0
  &END POTENTIAL
&END ATOM
